---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="ApopTosis AI — Business">
  <section class="container mx-auto py-16 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-garamond mb-8 text-center">ApopTosis AI — Business</h1>
    <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      Structured for renewal, not growth at all costs.
    </p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Revenue Streams</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
          <li>Subscriptions to PrimeFlux-Ai runtime ($99/month for pro features).</li>
          <li>Royalties from QuantaCoin transactions (1% on alignment proofs).</li>
          <li>Consulting for ethical AI governance (custom PrimeFlux integrations).</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Partnerships</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
          <li>xAI for networkless intelligence deployments.</li>
          <li>Open-source for researchers (PrimeFlux math on GitHub).</li>
          <li>Licensing PrimeFlux for industries (finance, defense, education).</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-lg max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      ApopTosis AI LLC is a Series LLC in Cheyenne, Wyoming — designed to prune and renew. We don't sell data. We don't lock users. We build systems that serve humanity.
    </p>
    <div class="text-center mt-8">
      <a href="/contact" class="bg-prime-gold text-prime-blue px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-opacity-80">Partner with Us</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
